high_descs: Walk into the living room and go next to the coffeetable.
Pick up the spoon that is on the coffee table.
Take the spoon to the sink.
Put the spoon in the bathroom sink.
Turn the water on and rise the spoon, then remove it from the sink.
Take the spoon with you and leave the sink.
anns.task_desc: Getting a spoon to wash in the sink.

high_descs: Turn your right side, take a walk towards the coffeetable
Take a spoon from the roundtable.
Turn your back and walk towards the bathroom and take a right turn and walk into the bathroom. Then turn left towards the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Turn towards your left and again reach the sink.
Place the spoon on the top of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the Spoon on the top of the Sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the coffee table
Take the spoon from the coffee table
Turn around and go near the sink
Put the spoon into the sink and washed it
Turn around and go near the sink table
Put the spoon on the sink table
anns.task_desc: Placed the spoon on the sink table
